    "synopsis": "One of the memories available in the Colony \"Brain Reader\" depicts how a colony uses the flesh of its victims to expand, like a living thing.",
    "how_to_trigger": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A- Use ReCon command \"oe MemLib_AllJars\" to get all the brain jars and teleport to the Brain Reading Device.- In front of you will be a severed head and a receptacle to its left. Insert the appropriate brain jar into the receptacle by interacting with it - the jar is called \"Butchered Mind\".- After inserting the jar, it will appear on top of the receptacle and you can talk to the severed head for the dialogue to start."
